strings: <voice_0x01001C5C><se_high>Princess Medea: Thank you for bringing me to the spring again, <hero>.
<voice_0x01001C5D><se_high>Princess Medea: Coming here is the only chance I get to relax and forget my troubles.

<voice_0x01001C5E><se_high>Princess Medea: I miss the time we spent together at the castle
so much...
<voice_0x01001C5F><se_high>Princess Medea: Do you remember when we first met, <hero>?
<voice_0x01001C60><se_high>Princess Medea: We were so small. I remember spending every waking hour together when we were children.
<voice_0x01001C61><se_high>Princess Medea: You were always running everywhere, <hero>. It took all of my energy just to keep up with you!

<voice_0x01001C62><se_high>Princess Medea: Oh! I can feel the spring water wearing off...
I hope we can talk again soon.
I'll miss you, <hero>!
